Title: Princess
Writer: Pirjo Toikka, Arto Halonen, Paavo Westerberg
Actors: Katja Küttner, Samuli Edelmann, Krista Kosonen, Peter Franzén
Plot: Princess tells the true story of former cabaret dancer Anna Lappalainen's redemptive struggle with insanity, who checked in to Finland's Kellokoski Psychiatric Hospital in 1945.
